          <fr:mainmatter><fr:p>The cartesian product of <fr:link href="jms-00MH.xml" title="Countable set" addr="jms-00MH" type="local">countable</fr:link> sets is <fr:link href="jms-00MH.xml" title="Countable set" addr="jms-00MH" type="local">countable</fr:link>.</fr:p>
 
   
